<BaseLayout title="christopher joy — researcher">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>christopher j. joy</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">researcher &middot; consultant &middot; southeast asia</p>
  </div>
  <hr class="rule-accent" />

  <p>
    I'm Christopher — a consultant and researcher interested in developing economies with a
    particular focus on Southeast Asia's rapid growth and economic rise. I consider my work
    interdisciplinary, pulling from such diverse areas as female empowerment, poverty reduction,
    the region's political economies and state-society relations, and, on occasion, international
    macroeconomics. I have spent significant portions of the last decade in Southeast Asia and
    speak Vietnamese, Indonesian, and Thai.
  </p>

  <p>
    My short resume is <a href="https://rxresu.me/chrisjoy/resume">here</a>.
  </p>

  <p class="contact">
